AGILE MODEL
---------------------------------------------------------------

* Build little by little and improve as u go .
Waterfall: One-time sequence → Requirements → Design → Build → Test → Release
Agile: Repeating cycle → Plan → Build → Test → Review → Repeat
-------------------------------------------------------------




🌊 Waterfall: A step-by-step software development method where each phase is done one after another.
🔄 Agile: A method where software is built in small parts with continuous improvement.
⚙️ DevOps: A practice that combines development and operations to deliver software quickly and continuously.


